Next Steps
The next steps for the analysis will be:
- Work on cleaning, categorising, and analysing the other mutations, increased mitotic activity values, and lobes involved.
- Looking at how these variables may interact and influence each other and the corresponding survival time.
- Meeting with my professor next week to discuss any avenues of analysis I may be missing to ensure that all of the data work is strong.
